e and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, cats are not impure, as they meander around you.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"It is the majority opinion of the scholars among the companions of the Prophet (s\u0323), the successors, and those after them such as Al-Shafi'i,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38657,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/01\/26\/dead-wailing\/","url_meta":{"origin":5692,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Dead are tortured by wailing over them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 26, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe deceased are tormented by their families wailing over them.\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cI hope he would be spared from that if he prohibited them while he was alive.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1002 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32727,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/09\/martyrs-protected-pain-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":5692,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Martyrs protected from pain of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe martyr does not feel the pain of being killed except as one of you feels the pinch of an insect bite.\u201d Source: S